<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Service Voucher</title>

<style>
body{
    font-family: Arial, "Noto Naskh Arabic", "Amiri", Tahoma, sans-serif;
    background:#f2f2f2;
    margin:0;
}

.wrapper{
    width:1000px;
    margin:20px auto;
    background:#fff;
    padding:20px;
    border:1px solid #000;
}

.header-table{
    width:100%;
    border-collapse:collapse;
    margin-bottom:10px;
}

.header-table td{
    border:none;
    vertical-align:middle;
}

.logo{
    height:70px;
}

.center-title{
    text-align:center;
}

.center-title h2{
    margin:0;
    font-size:20px;
}

.service-title{
    text-align:center;
    font-weight:bold;
    letter-spacing:3px;
    margin-top:5px;
}

table{
    width:100%;
    border-collapse:collapse;
    font-size:12px;
    margin-top:5px;
}

table, th, td{
    border:1px solid #000;
    text-align:center;
}

th, td{
    padding:5px;
}

.section-heading{
    text-align:center;
    font-weight:bold;
    margin-top:10px;
    letter-spacing:2px;
}

.center{text-align:center;}
.right{text-align:right;}

.qr-wrapper{
    margin-top:10px;
}

.note{
    font-size:11px;
    margin-top:8px;
    white-space:pre-line;
}

.arabic-block{
    direction:rtl;
    text-align:right;
    font-size:13px;
    margin-top:8px;
    font-family: "Noto Naskh Arabic","Amiri",Tahoma,Arial;
}

.important{
    margin-top:10px;
    border-top:2px solid #000;
    padding-top:5px;
    font-size:12px;
}

.qr-image{
    width:260px;
    height:260px;
    background:#fff;
}

@media print {
    body{
        background:#fff;
    }

    .wrapper{
        width:760px;
        margin:0 auto;
        padding:8px;
    }

    .logo{
        height:52px;
    }

    .center-title h2{
        font-size:18px;
    }

    .center-title p{
        margin:2px 0;
        font-size:10px;
        line-height:1.25;
    }

    .service-title{
        margin-top:3px;
        font-size:11px;
        letter-spacing:1.5px;
    }

    table{
        margin-top:4px;
        font-size:10px;
    }

    th, td{
        padding:3px 4px;
        font-size:10px;
    }

    .section-heading{
        margin-top:6px;
        font-size:10px;
        letter-spacing:1px;
    }

    .qr-wrapper{
        margin-top:6px;
    }

    .qr-wrapper ul{
        margin:4px 0 0 14px;
        padding:0;
    }

    .qr-wrapper li{
        margin-bottom:2px;
        font-size:9.5px;
        line-height:1.2;
    }

    .qr-image{
        width:210px;
        height:210px;
    }

    .note,
    .arabic-block,
    .important{
        margin-top:4px;
        font-size:8.5px;
        line-height:1.15;
    }

    .arabic-block{
        font-size:9px;
        line-height:1.25;
    }
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="wrapper">

<!-- HEADER -->
<table class="header-table">
<tr>
<td width="20%">
    <% if(company.logo){ %>
        <img src="<%= company.logo %>" class="logo">
    <% } %>
</td>

<td width="60%" class="center-title">
    <h2><%= company.name.toUpperCase() %></h2>
    <div><p>Shaheen View Appartments, Office #7, Mezzanine floor, Shaheen View, off Shahrah e Faisal, Block-6 Block 6 P.E.C.H.S., Karachi, 76800</p></div>
    <div class="service-title">SERVICE VOUCHER</div>
</td>

<td width="20%" class="right">
    <% if(foreignCompany.logo){ %>
        <img src="<%= foreignCompany.logo %>" class="logo">
    <% } %>
</td>
</tr>
</table>

<!-- VOUCHER INFO -->
<table>
<tr>
<td><strong>UMRAH COMPANY</strong></td>
<td><%= foreignCompany.name %></td>
<td><strong>HOTEL VOUCHER#</strong></td>
<td><%= voucher.voucherNo %></td>
<td><strong>V-DATE</strong></td>
<td><%= voucher.date %></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Executive Agent</strong></td>
<td colspan="5">PKG CATEGORY / DAZ 0%</td>
</tr>
</table>

<!-- PARTY DETAILS -->
<div class="section-heading">PARTY DETAILS</div>

<table>
<tr>
<th>SR</th>
<th>PAX NAME(S)</th>
<th>PASSPORT NO.</th>
<th>GROUP</th>
<th>VISA NO.</th>
</tr>

<% customers.forEach((c,i)=>{ %>
<tr>
<td class="center"><%= i+1 %></td>
<td><%= c.name %></td>
<td><%= c.passport %></td>
<td>901052165</td>
<td><%= c.visaNumber %></td>
</tr>
<% }) %>

<tr>
<td colspan="5" class="center">
GENTS: <%= customers.filter(c=>c.gender==='male').length %> &nbsp;&nbsp;
LADIES: <%= customers.filter(c=>c.gender==='female').length %> &nbsp;&nbsp;
CHILDREN: <%= customers.filter(c=>c.paxType==='children').length %> &nbsp;&nbsp;
INFANT: <%= customers.filter(c=>c.paxType==='infant').length %> &nbsp;&nbsp;
TOTAL PAX: <%= customers.length %>
</td>
</tr>
</table>

<!-- ACCOMMODATION -->
<div class="section-heading">ACCOMMODATION DETAILS</div>

<table>
<tr>
<th>CITY</th>
<th>HOTEL NAME</th>
<th>ROOM</th>
<th>ROOM TYPE</th>
<th>CHECK IN</th>
<th>CHECK OUT</th>
<th>NIGHTS</th>
</tr>

<% hotels.forEach(h=>{ %>
<tr>
<td><%= h.city %></td>
<td><%= h.name %></td>
<td class="center">1</td>
<td><%= h.roomType %></td>
<td><%= h.checkIn %></td>
<td><%= h.checkOut %></td>
<td class="center"><%= h.nights %></td>
</tr>
<% }) %>

<tr>
<td colspan="6" class="right"><strong>Total Nights</strong></td>
<td class="center">
<%= hotels.reduce((sum,h)=>sum+h.nights,0) %>
</td>
</tr>
</table>

<!-- TRANSPORT -->
<div class="section-heading">TRANSPORTATION DETAILS</div>

<table>
<tr>
<th>TYPE</th>
<th>ROUTE</th>
</tr>

<% transports.forEach(t=>{ %>
<tr>
<td><%= t.type %></td>
<td><%= t.route %></td>
</tr>
<% }) %>
</table>

<!-- FLIGHT DETAILS -->
<div class="section-heading">FLIGHT DETAILS</div>

<table>
<tr>
<th>FLIGHT</th>
<th>FROM</th>
<th>TO</th>
<th>DEPARTURE</th>
<th>ARRIVAL</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><%= departureFlight.flightNo %></td>
<td><%= departureFlight.fromCity %></td>
<td><%= departureFlight.toCity %></td>
<td><%= departureFlight.date %> - <%= departureFlight.takeoff %></td>
<td><%= departureFlight.date %> - <%= departureFlight.landing %></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><%= arrivalFlight.flightNo %></td>
<td><%= arrivalFlight.fromCity %></td>
<td><%= arrivalFlight.toCity %></td>
<td><%= arrivalFlight.date %> - <%= arrivalFlight.takeoff %></td>
<td><%= arrivalFlight.date %> - <%= arrivalFlight.landing %></td>
</tr>
</table>

<!-- QR + CONTACT -->
<table class="qr-wrapper">
<tr>
<td width="70%" style="text-align: left;">
    <strong>Notes.</strong>
    <ul>
        <li>MAKKAH HOTEL: Uzair 0548335007 (Day) Tariq 0549306332 (Night)</li>
        <li>MEDINAH HOTEL: MR. ARSALAN +966544809146</li>
        <li>Transport Contact: +966500000000</li>

        <% if (notes) { %>
            <% notes.split('\n').forEach(n => { %>
                <li><%= n %></li>
            <% }) %>
        <% } %>
    </ul>
</td>

<td width="30%" class="center">
<img src="<%= qrImage %>" class="qr-image"><br>
<strong>AUTHORIZED<br><%= company.name.toUpperCase() %></strong>
</td>
</tr>
</table>

<!-- NOTES -->
<div class="note">
<strong>Note:</strong><br>
- Please contact Makkah/Madinah operations 24 hours before the scheduled transportation and notify them accordingly.
- Room sharing means 4-6 beds per room.
- Separate room will incur extra cost.
- If the above mentioned hotel is unavailable in that case a similar category hotel will be provided.
- In case of any transport related delays, our esteemed passengers are advised to observe patience at airports and hotels.
- Each and every Pax has to wear wrist band or company badge. If anybody fails to follow directions SAR 2,000 will be charged as penalty per Pax.
- Please when you call for requesting Transportation or any services you must give us the Name of the Agency and the Serial Number above.
- No, service will be provided if the vendor fails to notify us the agency name and the serial number
</div>

<!-- ARABIC BLOCK -->
<div class="arabic-block">
تنبيه هام: يمنع تسليم جواز السفر لأي شخص داخل المملكة العربية السعودية سواء وكيل أو شركة نقل.
يرجى التواصل مع وكيل السفر الباكستاني في حال حدوث أي مشكلة.
</div>

<div class="important">
<strong>IMPORTANT NOTICE:</strong>
Passengers are requested not to hand over your passport to anyone in Saudi Arabia either agent or transporter provider.
</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
